        <cap:headline>Flood Warning in effect </cap:headline>
        <cap:description>
            AT 1:00 PM MST...According to the (12:30) hr M.S.T observation today, the water level of Bago River at Bago is observed as (36) cm (about 1-foot) below its danger level. It may reach its danger level during the next (48) hours commencing noon today.
        </cap:description>
        <cap:instruction>Take cover in a substantially higher place or mountain area until the stop passess.</cap:instruction>
